OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine and dry
OL,6,Fthrough the evening with increasingly
OL,7,Fhazy sunshine as cloud builds from the
OL,8,Fwest. Cloud will break at times
OL,9,Fovernight, giving some clearer spells
OL,10,Fand allowing temperatures to fall to
OL,11,Flow single figures in places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FAnother fine and likely dry
OL,14,Fday with patchy cloud. Given lighter
OL,15,Fwinds and frequent sunny spells it
OL,16,Fwill feel warmer than on Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
