OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FTurning cooler Thursday, with showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain by day, clearing
OL,8,Fovernight. Likely staying dry Friday
OL,9,Fwith sunny spells, but increasingly
OL,10,Fbreezy. Rain into Saturday clearing to
OL,11,Fa bright day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
